{"tid":786204,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[神作] 啱啱睇完神作GUN道 其實唔差","createTime":"2018-08-19T18:07:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T07:07:06.000Z","uid":8307,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"343bd4e595a2d6fd7ad44959f406357d04822139","tid":786204,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T18:07:51.000Z","msg":"GUN道呢套野出左十二年,呢套野都花費左十二年時間諗點整<br />\n由雷朋三世個作者出品,早幾日會然言峰xx題起套野<br />\n今日終於睇完呢套神作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n架空戰國時代作品,世界觀有細心設定過<br />\n點解戰國時代會演變到GUN道咁既樣<br />\n<br />\n套野出名作畫有超時代既水準,呢一張已經係成套野入面最唔靚仔既畫面黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/736x/01/d6/b0/01d6b03d9612a72a6505f9beb8ceecbc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2F736x%2F01%2Fd6%2Fb0%2F01d6b03d9612a72a6505f9beb8ceecbc.jpg&h=62e31550&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就算當笑片睇都幾好睇,水準超越終結的熾天使<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o1tYmCi5J2w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Do1tYmCi5J2w&d=Blq3pIHMKftc0vM4fysjGV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=0ea4c546\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o1tYmCi5J2w</a><br />\n<br />\n連日仔以前既2ch都稱呢套做傳說中既動畫<br />\n諗唔到呢套野有咩弱點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28c54c5a221d772ae41f82bc02ac71fb460ae517","tid":786204,"uid":147871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T18:08:14.000Z","msg":"樓豬入左新動漫谷未"},{"pid":"55d3627ee06526aab27cd1170a3e1b8a93c9d48c","tid":786204,"uid":8307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"28c54c5a221d772ae41f82bc02ac71fb460ae517","tid":786204,"uid":147871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T18:08:14.000Z","msg":"樓豬入左新動漫谷未"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T18:09:08.000Z","msg":"收聲啦龜sir 拎夠我啲個人資料玩未<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/20/020857_c3d22b9bb39c0f73c3328a10567a620d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.l